Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Agbago Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Don Mauro S. Tumbocon Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 673
An Act Changing the Name of the Agbago Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Don Mauro S. Tumbocon Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Agbago Elementary School located in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, is changed to Don Mauro S. Tumbocon Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: Macrh 7, 1984
